title: Rangers beat Blue Jays in 14th to take 2-0 ALDS lead
text:
Published By: Fox News: Sports - Today 
Backup infielder Hanser Alberto singled home the go-ahead run in the 14th inning and the Texas Rangers beat the Toronto Blue Jays 6-4 Friday...
